Class AACLATMPacketizer

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class AACLATMPacketizer
extends AbstractPacketizer
implements java.lang.Runnable
    RFC 3640. Encapsulates AAC Access Units in RTP packets as specified in the RFC 3640. This packetizer is used by the AACStream class in conjunction with the MediaCodec API introduced in Android 4.1 (API Level 16).
